{"tid":1480140,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（世柒）BNO 六四 Trump 柏林危機","createTime":"2019-08-17T07:31:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T03:27:14.000Z","uid":21716,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a99a0b64254890ec7daa15f9abbe11506d8a763a","tid":1480140,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:31:22.000Z","msg":"由於習近平同林鄭月娥嘅腦袋問題，依家香港唔只玩出法國大革命，仲玩出柏林危機翻版，依家全西方國家都認為香港係柏林翻版，Trump自己都被人縛上戰車，唔打唔得。甚至BNO平權都係英國被縛上戰車，美國國家安全顧問 Bolton嘅警告十分清晰，習近平搞第二次 六四 就一定大鑊，大家都知點解連串變化點嚟。<br />\n<br />\nBNO 六四 Trump 柏林危機<br />\n<br />\n喺G20期間廣告戰係好重要，依家大家睇清楚點解，因為西方國家係會救咗大聲呼救果個，而香港人係竭盡全力呼救，一如當年嘅西柏林人，呢個亦係點解，最後玩出柏林危機翻版出嚟。所以BNO平權變成英國主權問題，唔再係中英聯合聲明或者國際條約問題，你中國唔honour國際條約，仲玩到柏林危機第二，所以依家英國人睬你都有味，就係BNO依家係國家主權問題，不容你中國說三道四，即係BNO最後一個平權障礙：中英聯合聲明英方備忘錄，已經不存在。<br />\n<br />\n而 Bolton 嘅 Warning，唔好再搞出第二個 六四 ，話美國仍然對1989年記憶猶新，更加反映美國人立場，美國人唔會再犯三十年前嘅錯誤，所以英國係必須十分之慷慨俾BNO甚至香港人英籍，因為一出事，好可能係直接軍事介入，柏林危機當時都幾乎玩到出事，係蘇聯人始終係知道有啲嘢玩太盡真係自己都玩唔起，所以去到就出事就退讓落嚟。所以最後至有柏林圍牆呢家嘢，好大程度上係美蘇戰略角力保護西柏林之下，最大嘅戰略結果。依家中國要諗清楚，如果英國突然宣布所有 BNO 及其後代係英國公民，真係會大打出手，而且係得到美國人同德國人支持，因為香港係東方西柏林，唔只係美國報紙USA Today講，係德國報章都咁講，喺呢件事上，德美絕對會同一陣線，唔會有講笑嘅空間。<br />\n<br />\n所以8月18日，如果有人以為可以玩鋪勁，我諗中國政府自己諗清楚， 依家美國民意強大到 Trump 都要做強硬派，甚至英國都要完全變硬，甚至呢次危機可能係冷戰之後最大鑊危機之一，你習近平同身邊啲友仔，對西方歷史同文化缺乏認知，以為有錢大X晒，依家錢又無，又無改進，西方俾足你班友120年時間，兩個甲子時間都係咁就返去早抖。<br />\n<br />\n所以連登仔有人號召，8月18日搞自由人鏈，好似當年波羅的海三國咁，我十分之同意，自由人鏈係另一件十分之觸動歐洲人嘅事件，自由人鏈係堅定咗歐洲支持波羅的海三國嘅立場，而香港同波羅的海三國共同點都係某程度上遭到出賣，依家當係找數。所以前蘇聯加盟共和國中，波羅的海三國迅速入歐盟係有原因。如果黑社會同克警敢對自由人鏈亂嚟，我睇後果極嚴重，唔講得笑。呢個絕對係爭取到西方電視畫面，應該做就係。甚至如果中國太離譜，歐洲整條西起巴黎，東至愛沙尼亞嘅人鏈聲援香港，我睇你中國仲可以點，你中國等變新蘇聯喇。<br />\n<br />\n所以有位曾經留德嘅教授，依家叫人散水，做法極不知所謂，依家係Berlin Blockade嘅翻版，依家散水邊個得益先？睇清楚熱普城果啲人嘅本質，信者得膠。"},{"pid":"bc74b7b7682943ef1ed45878ac45264d7abc6eb5","tid":1480140,"uid":58335,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:40:49.000Z","msg":"唔好燈啦<br />\n求下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3079f97cdd05c78051db2a06f69cbb2fd2372718","tid":1480140,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:41:14.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"07f8c1514ef7c67940c70ee36c2f9f08d60b8eaf","tid":1480140,"uid":143382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:44:01.000Z","msg":"所以818試下做人鏈？"},{"pid":"8b9932933864eac292583060cb521cd2109bee43","tid":1480140,"uid":276162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WCxPEcp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWCxPEcp.gif&h=95386393&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89a2963fef79c0a53a1bf533ecf077d673a76997","tid":1480140,"uid":209900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:50:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6d4125d35021260abde8569d9d53196815443ca","tid":1480140,"uid":308875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T10:07:24.000Z","msg":"英國重量級議員  促給港人完整英國國籍<br />\n<br />\n英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得同父母講簽左有咩好處<br />\n點解要簽?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.居英權  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.去美國唔洗簽證 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.英國係法治，非人治 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.民主自由 <br />\n5.房屋政策教好 <br />\n6. 去歐美國家入境時唔會被問長問短 <br />\n7. 00後可以用家庭團聚形式入籍 <br />\n8.攞到脫離現有被強加國籍啲條件<br />\n9.英國無再教育營<br />\n10.無2047問題<br />\n11.因為多左英國公民喺香港，英國政府會易D發聲<br />\n12.如取消左被強加國籍，可以喺香港call領事保護及用英國護照入境中國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPostal code 填000000<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=3aaf3202\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"9e94e64a84e7dcc9d1242452a60b762677838982","tid":1480140,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:13:50.000Z","msg":"簽名一分鐘，改變一生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be7a4e1a4a31ba02ede6725a18ff32bf751fc14","tid":1480140,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:16:46.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"65c1c1545d5174e7daee1a48d68388b2c3254c52","tid":1480140,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:17:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">818 和理非 着黑衫 帶gear 保護自己 砂布封右眼</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">完左遊行入機場</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n入嚟拎大量長輩圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480006</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78DSDkx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78DSDkx.jpg&h=223461c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W16AA7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW16AA7e.jpg&h=8266dbbe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oJEa9sf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoJEa9sf.jpg&h=7af30e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mn5xDkB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmn5xDkB.jpg&h=703812d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttTn0yX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttTn0yX.jpg&h=53df5d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEGdmre.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEGdmre.gif&h=aac3cc53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 七大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」</code></pre>"},{"pid":"e47e2c320f821040e926873dd75f5deb6c08f5c2","tid":1480140,"uid":209248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩都要 人鏈壯舉 全界焦點 可以試 <br />\n因為咩都要行下"},{"pid":"597766983d47160244651c6400fa87323c340598","tid":1480140,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:58:22.000Z","msg":"求求00後都幫手簽, 對你地都有好處<br />\n<br />\n英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍<br />\n<br />\n英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解要支持?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.成功爭取父母啲BNO變BC後, 因關係可以用家庭團聚形式入籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.增加香港有外國國籍啲人數, 提升外國政府啲話語權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.因中共反對, 所以我地更加要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.中共話香港人都是中國公民, 唔通你地想一世都係中國公民?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPostal code 就打000000<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u